<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
    <title>Nature Music Show</title>
</head>

<body>

    <center>

        <h1>Nature Music Show</h1>

        <h2>The nature stage is ready!</h2>

        <p>
            Play the music and enjoy the beautiful nature scenes with relaxing sounds.
        </p>

        <audio controls loop>
            <source src="music.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
            Your browser does not support the audio tag.
        </audio>

        <br><br>

        <video width="500" height="350" controls poster="poster.png" loop>
            <source src="aqua.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>

        <h2>The nature show is live!</h2>

        <p>
            This webpage uses the audio tag for music and the video tag to display beautiful nature videos.
        </p>

    </center>

</body>

</html>
